Online Writer 
The late Manicaland Provincial Affairs Minister, Dr Ellen Gwaradzimba has been declared a national heroine. This comes after Zanu PF Manicaland province had written to the party’s Politburo requesting that Gwaradzimba be accorded national heroine status. Gwaradzimba succumbed to Covid-19 at a Harare health facility Friday morning where she was admitted. More deatils to follow…